b:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Feature Analysis"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"Both Help Scout and Ultimate.ai share a solid foundation of core features including Live Chat, Ai Chatbot, Knowledge Base, Analytics. Where Help Scout pulls ahead is with exclusive access to Ticket Management, which can be a deciding factor for teams that rely on this capability. \n\nLooking at user ratings, Help Scout holds an overall score of 8/10 and an ease of use score of 9/10, while Ultimate.ai scores 7/10 overall and 5/10 for ease of use. These ratings reflect real user experiences and can indicate differences in usability, support quality, and overall satisfaction."}]]}]
c:["$","div",null,{"className":"prose","children":[["$","h2",null,{"children":"Pricing Breakdown"}],["$","p",null,{"children":"When it comes to pricing, Ultimate.ai comes in at a lower starting price of Custom, while Help Scout begins at $50/mo. Neither platform offers a free plan, so you will need to budget for at least the starting tier from the beginning. Be sure to take advantage of any trial periods they may offer."}]]}]
